data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch situated on over 6 acres of picturesque Lawrence countryside. Perched atop a hill, this property offers breathtaking views from every room. Upon entry, you're greeted by a spacious & inviting open floor plan on the main level, boasting stunning updates throughout. The living room, dining area, & kitchen flow seamlessly, with sliders leading out to the back deck. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with modern amenities, including a convenient snack bar, elegant butcher block countertops, stunning white cabinetry, & a stylish tile backsplash. Adjacent to the kitchen, a mudroom features convenient main floor laundry. Just down the hall, you'll find 3 cozy bedrooms & 2 beautifully updated baths, including the spacious primary suite. Venture downstairs to the lower level walkout, where a large rec room awaits, complete with brand new carpeting throughout & a cozy wood-burning stove. Outside, you'll find a private & wooded backyard offering endless possibilities & ample space to enjoy from every angle. Additional features of this home include a new furnace installed in 2023 & a new pressure tank added in 2022, providing peace of mind & efficiency. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home, where every day feels like a countryside retreat. Schedule your showing today!
